#. js-lingui-id: Wie492
#: src/case-studies/case-study-stories.ts
msgid "The business development team finally had the CRM they had been asking for. Adoption came naturally: their data was already there when they logged in."
msgstr "业务拓展团队终于拥有了他们一直想要的 CRM。采用过程顺理成章：当他们登录时，数据早已在其中。"

#. js-lingui-id: 2kHqXc
#: src/case-studies/case-study-stories.ts
msgid "The CEO had resisted bringing in a CRM for years. The business development team had no experience using one, and the licensing costs of well-known CRMs like Salesforce or HubSpot were hard to justify without any guarantee of adoption: CRMs are only as good as the maintenance of the data inside them."
msgstr "CEO 多年来一直抗拒引入 CRM。业务拓展团队也没有使用 CRM 的经验，而 Salesforce 或 HubSpot 等知名 CRM 的授权成本，在没有采用率保证的前提下很难被证明是合理的：CRM 的价值取决于其中数据被维护得有多好。"

#. js-lingui-id: EYi+kT
#: src/case-studies/case-study-stories.ts
msgid "The CRM as a *control hub*"
msgstr "作为*控制枢纽*的 CRM"

#. js-lingui-id: 2sfVd8
#: src/case-studies/case-study-stories.ts
msgid "The CRM as a control hub"
msgstr "作为控制枢纽的 CRM"

#. js-lingui-id: XlFsoH
#: src/case-studies/case-study-stories.ts
msgid "The early bet on the architecture is holding, and upcoming AI features are expected to make it even more relevant."
msgstr "对架构的早期押注正在发挥作用，即将到来的 AI 功能有望让这一架构变得更具价值。"

#. js-lingui-id: kCUcnD
#: src/sections/testimonials/partner-testimonials.data.ts
msgid "The flexibility is just amazing. Literally, there's nothing you cannot do. You can create objects, access everything through the API, pull notes and send them to the portal. Try doing that in HubSpot. No way. It's the true ability to build exactly what's actually needed."
msgstr "这种灵活性简直令人惊叹。从字面意义上说，没有什么是你做不到的。你可以创建对象，通过 API 访问一切，将笔记拉取出来并发送到门户。试着在 HubSpot 里这么做——根本不可能。真正关键的是，它让你有能力精确构建真正需要的东西。"

#. js-lingui-id: MaHqAc
#: src/sections/testimonials/testimonials.data.ts
#: src/case-studies/case-study-stories.ts
msgid "The flexibility is really what made the difference. Our needs evolve very fast. I discover a new need and in two clicks I can address it. That is a real advantage when you are moving quickly."
msgstr "真正产生差异的是这种灵活性。我们的需求变化非常快。我发现一个新需求，只需点两下就能解决。当你在高速前进时，这是真正的优势。"

#. js-lingui-id: Q5iZ9Q
#: src/case-studies/case-study-stories.ts
msgid "The flexibility to wire this together, without outside help and without fighting the platform, is what made it possible for a single person to stand up and maintain a connected stack across an entire consultancy."
msgstr "能够把这一切连在一起，而无需外部帮助、也不用与平台对抗，正是让一个人就可以为整家咨询公司搭建并维护互联技术栈的关键。"

#. js-lingui-id: l0eUFC
#: src/case-studies/case-study-stories.ts
msgid "The full rollout landed in July 2025. Since then, Nine Dots built a Smart Assistant on top of the system, nudging agents with tasks, reminders, and on-demand market analysis. Some agents never open Twenty directly, yet they are powered by it, outperforming peers on manual processes alone. By Q1 2026, Homeseller had recorded its best sales quarter ever."
msgstr "全面上线于 2025 年 7 月完成。从那以后，Nine Dots 在该系统之上构建了 Smart Assistant，通过任务、提醒和按需的市场分析来提示经纪人。一些经纪人从未直接打开 Twenty，但他们依然由其驱动，仅凭这些就能在以手工为主的流程上明显胜过同行。到 2026 年 Q1，Homeseller 创下了有史以来最好的销售季度。"

